{
  "texts": [
    "We ran MobMess to analyse the 226,194 predicted plasmid contigs.",
    "MobMess grouped the contigs into a total of 132,616 clusters.",
    "Of these, 64,266 clusters were 'fragment clusters' that contained 125,475 contigs, which we interpreted as assembly fragments of other predicted plasmids.",
    "We discarded these fragments from further analysis.",
    "The other 68,350 clusters were non-fragment clusters (that is, 1,169 backbone and 67,181 maximal clusters) and contained 100,719 contigs."
  ]
}